Module it.polimi.ingsw
Package it.polimi.ingsw.server.controller.save

Class SaveFileData

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.server.controller.save.SaveFileData
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class SaveFileData extends Object implements Serializable
This object contains all the information needed to completely store the state of a running game on the disk. For a game state to be safely stored, the following elements are needed:

GAME MODEL INFORMATION

  • A List of all the players, saved in a simplified way, as a list of SimplifiedPlayer objects. Each SimplifiedPlayer contains the achievements and a simplified description of the shelf (as a matrix) and of the associated personal goal card
  • The board, saved as a matrix
  • All the information about the game, saved as a SimplifiedGameInfo object.
  • The game sack, saved as a Sack object.

GAME CONTROLLER INFORMATION

  • The ordered list of nicknames
  • The index in the list of players of the active player
Author:
Luca Guffanti
